FY_DUST_01
----------

It took much time to do the map. I tried to do it as soon as possible because I may have to offline for months (my learning schedule is full! :(( )
This maps is quite large that made me tired doing the whole thing. However, I think It's good to be a fight yard. But I did not add any weapons or buyzones into it. You may need DM to have good day with it.
And It's original. You will need to builcubemaps before playing to get correct cubemaps. Having trouble with 3D Skybox so I copy and tag Valve for 3D Skybox. Of course, I have done some parts, not copy all :p!!
I also do the radar and overview. But as I said, too tired, so nav is still empty. Be patient to build nav file for your own (doesn't require :)
Thanks TopHATTwaffle for his great tutorials.

Now, enjoy, comment and vote for me :D

Fy_dust_mute [BETA RELEASE 1]
----------------by iMute
-------------------------------------------
CURRENT VERSION: fy_dust_mute_b2
-----------
INFO
-----------

fy_dust_mute is a fight yard map made with de_dust/de_dust2 textures. This is only my second 
map, and I tried to use a few more effects than in my previous map. This is currently a beta release.

-----------
INSTALLATION
-----------

It's easy to install:

Extract the "maps" folder to...

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\YOURACCOUNTNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike

Then simply load up CS:S, create a server and choose fy_dust_mute. You can add some bots and test out
the gameplay (NAV file included), then comment on FPSB. ;)
------------
RELEASE
------------
b1 --- BETA RELEASE 1 [Original Release]
b2 --- BETA RELEASE 2 [Tower bug fixed, new textures
------------
Play fun! There are places to hide and seek. Enough weapons to all players.
Enjoy!

Okay. Here is the Beta version of FY_Dust
(http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/148356)
After working on this a while after reading PaiN_Agents great feedback, here's the result.
Aprox 1 week to do this Beta version.
Alot of credit to Valve.
Their 3D skybox, and De_dust Hall used, their soundscape.
This map has many many more features then the previouse version of FY_Dust.
-More props.
-More detail.
-Fixed tower/Beta.
-Fixed props.
-Lots of spawns, 40+
-Features as listed above & below.
-Still AI noded, works great with bots.
-More decals.
-Fixed CT's beeing able to spawnkill T's easily, multiple exits & spawns.
-Beta walls/fences.
-More lighting affects, wind & others..
-Wider, larger map. 
-More spawns for T & CT.
-Soundscapes. (Valves).
- Lots, lots more.
